snippet.title: Warcraft III: The Culling Campaign Trailer
snippet.description:
Warcraft III: Reforged will be available at 3 p.m. PST on January 28, 2020.

WAR HAS RETURNED: http://www.playwarcraft3.com 

The Culling of Stratholme: The story of Prince Arthas' attempt to save his people using any means necessary - only to lose them all, and himself, to darkness.
---- 
Warcraft III: Reforged is a stunning reimagining of the revolutionary real-time strategy game that laid the foundation for Azeroth’s most epic stories. 

Pre-Purchase Now: https://blizz.ly/war3shop
Like us on Facebook – http://www.facebook.com/playwarcraft3 
Follow us on Twitter – http://www.twitter.com/warcraft3
